OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FScottish education         
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fperformance falling, says  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fstudy                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Performance in Scotland's high schools 
OL,6, has slipped according to new           
OL,7, international research on education.   
OL,9,FThe Pisa report measures education     
OL,10,Fstandards among nearly 700,000         
OL,11,F15-year-olds worldwide.                
OL,13,FThe report shows a long-term decline in
OL,14,FScotland's performance in reading,     
OL,15,Fmaths and science.                     
OL,17,FScottish ministers said Covid          
OL,18,Frestrictions had a "profound impact" on
OL,19,Feducation, and since the study there   
OL,20,Fhad been further evidence of recovery. 
